## Specific Areas to Investigate

### Typography
- Font families (serif, sans-serif, monospace)
- Font sizes (heading hierarchy)
- Line height and spacing
- Letter spacing
- Font weights (light, regular, medium, bold)
- Reading width (optimal line length)

### Editor Capabilities
- Rich text: bold, italic, underline, strikethrough
- Lists: bullet, numbered, checklist
- Headings: H1, H2, H3
- Code blocks: inline and multi-line
- Quotes
- Horizontal rules
- Tables
- Inline images
- Links (internal and external)
- Embeds (video, etc.)

### UI Chrome
- Toolbar: location, style, behavior
- Sidebar: folders, tags, search
- Title handling
- Breadcrumbs
- Metadata (date created, modified, word count)
- Focus mode (distraction-free)

### Interactions
- Click to edit vs always editable
- Keyboard shortcuts
- Drag and drop
- Auto-save indicators
- Smooth animations
- Loading states

### Organization
- Folders and subfolders
- Tags
- Favorites/pins
- Search and filters
- Recent notes
- Trash/archive

